values:
I love this definition of 'slumber':

"a natural and periodic state of rest during which consciousness of the world is suspended"

I found my last Kinstone Fusion!

Yes!

*does happy dance*

Politeness and compromise are diabolic
 
Everyday we must haggle with our inner demon to not say everything we think for there are limits to what people can take
 
Lets be bastards and let people run away in all directions screaming in agony and angry at us for doing as they said

Evil ending of the fourth season of alias!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!


evilevilevilevilevilevilevilevilevilevilevilevilevil!!!!!!!!!

*is incoherent*

It snowed today!
Yay! My garden was covered in snow! And I almost slipped while wakling down the road to the train station... *laughs* That's most probably because I was in a hurry 'cause once again *rolls eyes* I'd gone out of the house in a rush. Though this time even more so than usual 'cause I'd overslept and I only had 10 minutes to get ready... when I usually spend 15 in the bathroom just waking up *laughs*

Hahahahahaha! My mom and sis try to speak in whispers 2 meters away from me on things concerning my bday... Them: ...tomorrow...elsa...bday...me too... Me: *silent laughter* Them: ...couldn't find a pink bow... Me: PINK BOW!!!!!!!!!!!! Them *agahst* how come she has so good hearing? Me: *finds it hilarious* *can't stop laughing* Them: *flee* Me: HAHAHAHAHA! Pink Bow!!!!!

It's much too cold...

*looks at her currently freezing feet*

*wiggles her toes*
*still feels them... for now*

And we're not even in winter!

*counts layers*
1...
2...
3...
4!

Maybe I need another pair of socks?
Or mittens?
Though then it'll be a bit hard to write on the keyboard.

*sees herself bundled up so well that only the tip of her nose pokes out and she tries to write with that*

*laughs*

No.. I guess I'll have to forgo the extra layer and make my dog sit on my feet to warm them up :)
Figured out why HP and the GoF is rated PG-13? The Onion makes an educated guess... And definitely a hilarious one *super large grin* Check it out!

*does wild dance* yes!yes!yes! *punches fist in the air* *several times* mwahahaha! Red Sox regain share of first place take me out to the ball game! buy me some peanuts and crackerjacks! I don't care if I ever come back!

my very first post
*is all excited*

little bits of randomness:

i'm still trying to find out everything but i'm sure there's a manual lying around here somewhere...

i was just given a free period so i'm in a good mood, and then there's sailing to look forward to!

though i have theater after and i don't know my text well *shifty eyes* maybe my teacher won't notice? /wishful thinking i know.../

i read on a LJ that LJ-ers (if such a word exists) love to talk about themselves, i agree most heartedly! as interesting *coughcough* as my life is i'm really doin this to talk, talk, talk (or in this case write, write, write) until it bores you to tears /possibly and my sis would say most certainly/
